+ * dpni_open() - Open a control session for the specified object
+ * @mc_io:	Pointer to MC portal's I/O object
+ * @cmd_flags:	Command flags; one or more of 'MC_CMD_FLAG_'
+ * @dpni_id:	DPNI unique ID
